  "explanation": [
    "Let <katex>$I = \\int_0^\\pi \\frac{x \\tan x}{\\sec x \\csc x} dx = \\int_0^\\pi x \\frac{\\sin x/\\cos x}{1/\\cos x \\cdot 1/\\sin x} dx = \\int_0^\\pi x \\sin^2 x dx$</katex>.",
    "Using <katex>$\\int_0^a f(x) dx = \\int_0^a f(a-x) dx$</katex>:",
    "<katex>$I = \\int_0^\\pi (\\pi-x) \\sin^2(\\pi-x) dx = \\int_0^\\pi (\\pi-x) \\sin^2 x dx$</katex>.",
    "<katex>$2I = \\int_0^\\pi (x + \\pi - x) \\sin^2 x dx = \\pi \\int_0^\\pi \\sin^2 x dx$</katex>.",
    "<katex>$\\int_0^\\pi \\sin^2 x dx = \\int_0^\\pi \\frac{1-\\cos 2x}{2} dx = \\frac{1}{2} [x - \\frac{\\sin 2x}{2}]_0^\\pi = \\frac{1}{2} (\\pi - 0) = \\frac{\\pi}{2}$</katex>.",
    "<katex>$2I = \\pi (\\frac{\\pi}{2}) = \\frac{\\pi^2}{2} \\implies I = \\frac{\\pi^2}{4}$</katex>."
